Hello, thank you for contacting Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. My name is Adam Hill. May I know your name, please?

Hi, Adam. My name is Lauren Flores.

Nice to meet you, Lauren. How can I assist you today with your complaint?

I had an issue with the yacht I recently purchased. There were some unexpected maintenance problems.

I apologize for any inconvenience, Lauren. Can I have your purchase order number to look into this further?

Sure, the purchase order number is one two three four five.

Thank you, Lauren. Could you also provide the model of the yacht so I can pull up the correct records?

It's the Ocean Breeze model.

I’ve found your details. I will investigate the issue and contact you with a resolution as soon as possible. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

No, that would be all. Thank you for your help, Adam.

You're welcome, Lauren. Thank you for your time and for bringing this to our attention. Have a great day!
